          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But if you turn away from them, they panic. When you take away their breath, they die and turn again to dust. "
        }
      ]
    },
